<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Alexei Batishchev | Academic & Art Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        /* Simple, clean styling */
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fcfcfc;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        h1 { margin: 0; font-weight: 600; color: #111; }
        p.subtitle { color: #666; font-style: italic; margin-top: 5px; }

        nav {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        nav a {
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #0066cc;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        section {
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        /* Art Gallery Grid */
        .gallery {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .gallery-item {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .gallery-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }

        .gallery-item .caption {
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #555;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Academic List styling */
        .academic-list {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .academic-list li {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .date { color: #888; font-size: 0.9em; }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Alexei Luka Batishchev</h1>
         <p class="subtitle">   <span style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #666; font-weight: normal; font-family: monospace;">[ɐlʲɪkˈsʲej ɫʊˈka bɐˈtʲiɕəf]</span> </p>
        <p class="subtitle">Linguist + Artist</p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#academic">Academic Work</a>
        <a href="#art">Art Portfolio</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>Welcome! I am a researcher and artist interested in [Your Interests]. This space holds a collection of my academic writing, current projects, and visual art.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="academic">
        <h2>Academic & Research</h2>
        <ul class="academic-list">
            <li>
                <strong>Project or Paper Title Here</strong> <span class="date">(2026)</span><br>
                Brief description of your research, conference presentation, or essay topic. 
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Another Academic Milestone Here</strong> <span class="date">(2025)</span><br>
                Details about your master's work, teaching experience, or specific sub-fields you focus on.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="art">
        <h2>Art Gallery</h2>
        <div class="gallery">
            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300" alt="Artwork description">
                <div class="caption">Artwork Title - Medium, Year</div>
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300" alt="Artwork description">
                <div class="caption">Artwork Title - Medium, Year</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Feel free to reach out via email at <strong>[first name] + [last name] + [at] + gmail [dot] com</strong> or follow my work on social media.</p>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Alexei Batishchev. Built with simple HTML/CSS.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
